Course Datasets

The following datasets will be used in the course:

airsat

Real data on the satisfaction and experience of 10,000 customers of an airline Info

# install.packages("readr")
airsat <- readr::read_csv("https://rb.gy/ldq0y4") |> print()

spotify

Real data on the popularity and acoustic properties of 5,000 songs from Spotify Info

# install.packages("readr")
spotify <- readr::read_csv("https://rb.gy/gmzeyv") |> print()

titanic

Real data on 1,309 passengers on the Titanic Info

# install.packages("readr")
titanic <- readr::read_csv("https://rb.gy/hm7p84") |> print()

water

Real data on the potability and chemical properties of 3,276 water bodies Info

# install.packages("readr")
water <- readr::read_csv("https://rb.gy/sjmiqr") |> print()
